125
00:18:17,850 --> 00:18:18,450
Shrimpie.

126
00:18:19,280 --> 00:18:20,860
Look at the fish I cured.

127
00:18:21,330 --> 00:18:21,790
Come on.

128
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,570
Give me some praise.

129
00:18:28,220 --> 00:18:29,750
What happened to your hand?

130
00:18:30,750 --> 00:18:32,480
Had too much to drink last night

131
00:18:33,110 --> 00:18:34,200
and took a spill.

132
00:18:34,530 --> 00:18:35,200
Let me see.

133
00:18:37,400 --> 00:18:38,200
Zhang Hailou.

134
00:18:40,380 --> 00:18:40,880
I...

135
00:18:49,740 --> 00:18:51,070
Come take a walk with me.

136
00:19:00,670 --> 00:19:03,250
[Gentle Breeze and Harmonious Air]

137
00:19:03,250 --> 00:19:07,010
[Qiyuan Tea Shop]

138
00:19:22,420 --> 00:19:23,020
Shrimpie,

139
00:19:23,500 --> 00:19:24,830
do you still remember
when we were in Nanyang,

140
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:26,420
and I really craved pork trotter noodles?

141
00:19:26,420 --> 00:19:28,220
We were too broke to afford them.

142
00:19:28,640 --> 00:19:30,790
And you told me we'd eat our fill
once we got back to Xiacheng.

143
00:19:30,790 --> 00:19:31,400
Look.

144
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,110
Haihua Grocery Store.

145
00:19:36,440 --> 00:19:39,010
Doesn't that sound exactly like
one of our family's businesses?

146
00:19:39,010 --> 00:19:39,870
It's right across the street.

147
00:19:39,870 --> 00:19:42,730
How about we buy this shop
and turn it into a pig farm?

148
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,790
Can't we afford pork trotter noodles

149
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:47,110
anytime we want now?

150
00:19:47,680 --> 00:19:49,550
Wouldn't it be a waste
to keep buying them?

151
00:19:49,550 --> 00:19:51,380
Besides, our mentor is so reckless.

152
00:19:51,380 --> 00:19:51,960
Who knows

153
00:19:51,980 --> 00:19:53,590
when she'll blow through
her entire nest egg?

154
00:19:53,590 --> 00:19:55,450
We've got to plan ahead, don't we?

155
00:19:56,540 --> 00:19:57,550
Three of us...

156
00:19:57,850 --> 00:20:00,050
T-Thirty pigs should be enough, right?

157
00:20:03,740 --> 00:20:05,600
Why have you been so quiet lately?

158
00:20:05,600 --> 00:20:06,580
Say something.

159
00:20:09,850 --> 00:20:10,650
Zhang Hailou.

160
00:20:18,750 --> 00:20:19,680
Actually, lately I've...

161
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:22,720
-Chief!
-Chief!

162
00:20:21,570 --> 00:20:22,900
[Haihua Grocery Store]

163
00:20:22,720 --> 00:20:24,070
Chief, we're here!

164
00:20:24,070 --> 00:20:25,130
You're here, kids.

165
00:20:27,350 --> 00:20:28,080
Stand still.

166
00:20:31,160 --> 00:20:33,010
They're just a bunch of kids
from the neighborhood.

167
00:20:33,010 --> 00:20:34,180
They practically idolize me.

168
00:20:34,180 --> 00:20:35,350
Pick out some good ones,

169
00:20:35,350 --> 00:20:38,350
and we can train them
as new recruits for our Archives.

170
00:20:40,730 --> 00:20:41,790
Alright, speak up—

171
00:20:42,110 --> 00:20:43,350
why did you come to me?

172
00:20:43,870 --> 00:20:46,790
Chief, he has a grievance to report!

173
00:20:47,980 --> 00:20:48,710
A grievance?

174
00:20:49,680 --> 00:20:50,480
Let's hear it.

175
00:20:52,570 --> 00:20:53,010
He...

176
00:20:55,140 --> 00:20:56,010
He's a bad guy!

177
00:20:57,140 --> 00:20:58,470
He wanted to kill my cat!

178
00:21:04,790 --> 00:21:06,540
Do you know what you're saying?

179
00:21:07,550 --> 00:21:08,550
Let me ask you all—

180
00:21:09,010 --> 00:21:10,480
